—ЩWarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/polars_arg-sort.mdЩ@489756867336f051d1ca852b44307ca937720019966dde101b9b8a1d13202842¶title: polars arg-sort‘ҐFlagsЩо``--reverse, -r``
: Reverse order.
``--nulls-last, -n``
: Nulls ordered last.
``--limit, -l {int}``
: Limit a sort output, this is for optimization purposes and might be ignored.
``--maintain-order, -m``
: Maintain order on sorted items.
’ђђЪ!Title: title: polars arg-sort
Path: Flags
Content:
``--reverse, -r``
: Reverse order.
``--nulls-last, -n``
: Nulls ordered last.
``--limit, -l {int}``
: Limit a sort output, this is for optimization purposes and might be ignored.
``--maintain-order, -m``
: Maintain order on sorted items.
